***REMOVED*** =============================================================================
***REMOVED*** Production Environment Configuration
***REMOVED*** =============================================================================
***REMOVED*** Residency Scheduler - Production deployment
***REMOVED***
***REMOVED*** IMPORTANT: Never commit actual secrets to version control
***REMOVED*** Copy this file to .env and fill in production values
***REMOVED*** =============================================================================

***REMOVED*** -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
***REMOVED*** Database Configuration
***REMOVED*** -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
DB_USER=scheduler
DB_NAME=residency_scheduler
***REMOVED*** Password is stored in secrets file, but can be set here for compose
DB_PASSWORD=CHANGE_ME_IN_PRODUCTION

***REMOVED*** -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
***REMOVED*** Security Configuration
***REMOVED*** -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
***REMOVED*** Secret key for JWT - generate with:
***REMOVED*** python -c "import secrets; print(secrets.token_urlsafe(64))"
SECRET_KEY=CHANGE_ME_GENERATE_SECURE_KEY

***REMOVED*** Redis password - generate with:
***REMOVED*** openssl rand -base64 32
REDIS_PASSWORD=CHANGE_ME_GENERATE_SECURE_PASSWORD

***REMOVED*** -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
***REMOVED*** Application Configuration
***REMOVED*** -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
***REMOVED*** Docker image tag
IMAGE_TAG=latest

***REMOVED*** Frontend port (80 for HTTP, 443 for HTTPS via reverse proxy)
FRONTEND_PORT=80

***REMOVED*** Backend API URL as seen from the frontend
***REMOVED*** Use /api for same-origin or full URL for cross-origin
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=/api

***REMOVED*** -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
***REMOVED*** CORS Configuration
***REMOVED*** -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
***REMOVED*** Allowed origins (JSON array format)
CORS_ORIGINS=["https://scheduler.example.com"]

***REMOVED*** -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
***REMOVED*** Data Storage Paths
***REMOVED*** -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
***REMOVED*** Base directory for persistent data
DATA_DIR=/var/lib/residency-scheduler

***REMOVED*** Directory containing secret files
SECRETS_DIR=./secrets

***REMOVED*** -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
***REMOVED*** Monitoring Configuration (Optional)
***REMOVED*** -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
***REMOVED*** Sentry DSN for error tracking
SENTRY_DSN=

***REMOVED*** -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
***REMOVED*** SSL/TLS Configuration (for reverse proxy)
***REMOVED*** -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
***REMOVED*** Set these if using external reverse proxy
***REMOVED*** SSL_CERT_PATH=/etc/ssl/certs/scheduler.crt
***REMOVED*** SSL_KEY_PATH=/etc/ssl/private/scheduler.key
